events.name: Alabama Crimson Tide at Missouri Tigers

headlines.description: Blake Sims threw a pair of touchdown passes and top-ranked Alabama pulled away in the fourth quarter to win its 24th Southeastern Conference championship with a 42-13 victory over No. 16 Missouri on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: Bama thumps Mizzou, takes home SEC

events.name: Iowa State Cyclones at TCU Horned Frogs

headlines.description: Trevone Boykin passed for a career-high 460 yards and caught a touchdown pass as TCU earned at least a share of the Big 12 championship and did nothing to hurt its case to be included in the College Football Playoff with a 55-3 win over Iowa State.
headlines.shortLinkText: TCU earns share of Big 12 title

events.name: Florida State Seminoles at Georgia Tech Yellow Jackets

headlines.description: Jameis Winston threw for 309 yards and three touchdowns, and Florida State (No. 4 CFP, No. 2 AP) held off Georgia Tech (No. 11 CFP, No. 12 AP) 37-35 Saturday night to win its third consecutive ACC championship.
headlines.shortLinkText: FSU stays perfect, wins ACC title

events.name: Wisconsin Badgers at Ohio State Buckeyes

headlines.description: Cardale Jones threw for 257 yards and three touchdowns, Ezekiel Elliott ran for a career-high 220 yards and two scores and No. 5 Ohio State made an emphatic statement with a 59-0 rout over No. 13 Wisconsin in Saturday's Big Ten championship game.

video.headline: Ohio State dominates Wisconsin in Big Ten title game

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Ohio State dominates Wisconsin in Big Ten title game) 2019/10/24 ESHEET SOTFULL

events.name: Kansas State Wildcats at Baylor Bears

headlines.description: Bryce Petty threw for 412 yards, Johnny Jefferson had two touchdown runs and sixth-ranked Baylor claimed a share of its second consecutive Big 12 title with a 38-27 win over ninth-ranked Kansas State on Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Baylor captures share of Big 12 title

events.name: Oklahoma State Cowboys at Oklahoma Sooners

headlines.description: Tyreek Hill returned a punt 91 yards for a touchdown with 45 seconds remaining to force overtime and Ben Grogan kicked a 21-yard field goal in the extra period to give Oklahoma State a 38-35 victory over No. 20 Oklahoma on Saturday.
headlines.shortLinkText: OK State rallies, sinks OU in OT

events.name: Fresno State Bulldogs at Boise State Broncos

headlines.description: Grant Hedrick ran for two touchdowns to lead No. 22 Boise State to a 28-14 victory over Fresno State to win the Mountain West Conference championship Saturday night.
headlines.shortLinkText: Hedrick leads No. 22 Boise St. to MWC title

headlines.description: Cincinnati beats Houston 38-31 for title share
headlines.shortLinkText: Cincinnati beats Houston 38-31 for title share

headlines.description: SMU avoids winless season, beating UConn 27-20
headlines.shortLinkText: SMU avoids winless season, beating UConn 27-20

events.name: Louisiana Tech Bulldogs at Marshall Thundering Herd

headlines.description: Rakeem Cato passed 5 yards to Deon-Tay McManus with 1:50 remaining to lift Marshall over Louisiana Tech 26-23 on Saturday for the Thundering Herd's first Conference-USA championship.
headlines.shortLinkText: Marshall rallies late to win 1st C-USA crown

headlines.shortLinkText: Coastal Carolina wins 36-15 in FCS playoffs
